com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.filter

Class JSONMapFilterRegEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.filter.AbstractJSONMapFilter
      • com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.filter.JSONMapFilterRegEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IJSONMapPreProcessor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FoDJSONMapFilterHasBugLink, SSCJSONMapFilterHasBugURL

    public class JSONMapFilterRegEx
extends AbstractJSONMapFilter
    This AbstractJSONMapFilter implementation allows for filtering JSONMap instances by evaluating the configured Pattern instances against the value for the corresponding JSON property path. If any of the Pattern doesn't match the corresponding property value, the given JSONMap instance is considered as 'not matching', and as a result (depending on the configured MatchMode) will be either included or excluded from further processing.
    Author:
    Ruud Senden
